DOC.brief_title: Laser Acupuncture Versus High Protein/Low Carbohydrate Diet Endothelial Markers Obese Females
DOC.detailed_description: Sixty females 20 year age body mass index ( BMI ) 30 kg/m2 divide three group ( 20 ) : two experimental group ( laser ; high protein low carbohydrate diet ) control . Each subject receive treatment relevant group , addition obtain 3 day dietary recall measurement include BMI , serum insulin endothelial marker . Laser control group receive 24 activated sham laser acupuncture treatment . High protein low carbohydrate group instruct take tailor high protein/low carbohydrate diet .
